Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.45,0:00:04.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ladies and gentlemen,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.94,0:00:08.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I bring you marvelous illusions that \Nmake this town sparkle at night!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.18,0:00:12.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please enjoy the last miraculous \Npresent of the year!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.19,0:00:24.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,K-Kid the Phantom Thief! \NWhere are you going?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.28,0:00:27.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Inspector Nakamori.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.02,0:00:49.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately, I don't have time \Nto toy with you anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.98,0:00:51.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.12,0:00:54.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.72,0:01:16.76,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Drink. Drive. Lose Your License.\NTake Precautions Against Fire
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.15,0:01:18.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Inspector!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.85,0:01:22.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.38,0:01:26.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's been gone for three months!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.64,0:01:30.52,Signs - readability,,0000,0000,0000,,The Phantom Thief Has Vanished\NThree months since \NKid the Phantom Thief's last crime\NRetired?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.45,0:01:30.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where the hell is he? Where?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.92,0:01:33.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did he go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.64,0:01:36.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just been three months. \NMaybe he hasn't gone anywhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.52,0:01:37.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.94,0:01:43.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Has he ever taken this much time off \Nbetween robberies?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.80,0:01:45.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, no, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.75,0:01:47.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Something's strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.01,0:01:49.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There must be a reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.92,0:01:49.67,Signs - readability,,0000,0000,0000,,Three months since \NKid the Phantom Thief's last crime
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.02,0:01:55.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But, Inspector, isn't it a good thing that \NKid the Phantom Thief isn't busy stealing?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.31,0:01:57.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what I'm saying!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.70,0:01:59.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna catch Kid with my own hands...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.55,0:02:06.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But it sounds like you want \NKid the Phantom Thief to commit crimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.28,0:02:08.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I should tell the commissioner...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.81,0:02:11.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, I don't think you need to go that far.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.18,0:02:12.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.43,0:02:17.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, say what you will. \NWe owe Inspector Nakamori a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.44,0:02:23.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When we switched shifts on that \Nlast stakeout, he brought me ramen.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.14,0:02:25.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He brought me a beef bowl.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.82,0:02:28.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.37,0:02:32.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to give serious thought \Nas to why Kid hasn't shown up lately!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.90,0:02:34.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.57,0:02:36.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He probably has a cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.46,0:02:41.01,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Drink. Drive. Lose Your License.\NTake Precautions Against Fire
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.89,0:02:40.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you guys morons?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.99,0:04:24.53,Signs - Thief Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,0)}Holy Night: Two Kid the Phantom Thieves!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.53,0:04:29.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh. First I get a cold, then finals...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.53,0:04:32.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This sucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.06,0:04:33.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.29,0:04:37.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought idiots were too slow\N to catch a cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.50,0:04:42.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't touch me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.97,0:04:46.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! I was worried about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.24,0:04:48.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make me laugh, jackass!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.54,0:04:55.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez! You're in a bad mood, Dad's in a snit \Nbecause Kid's been a no-show lately...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.10,0:04:56.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to worry about both of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.84,0:04:59.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's mad about Kid's {\i1}absence{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.15,0:05:03.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd think the cops would have no \Nproblem with a thief {\i1}not{\i0} stealing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.49,0:05:07.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad thinks it's weird that Kid hasn't \Nbeen around for three months now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.03,0:05:10.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like your old man's the weird one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.48,0:05:15.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure even Kid the Phantom Thief doesn't \Nfeel like stealing from time to time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.02,0:05:19.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, I've got my own problems to deal with.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.32,0:05:23.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Jii-chan, who always gathers \Nintel on the Big Jewels,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.54,0:05:26.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,was bedridden after straining his back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.67,0:05:31.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito, blow your nose.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.44,0:05:32.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.30,0:05:33.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.88,0:05:39.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Still, I wonder where that \Nsneak thief is hiding...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.94,0:05:45.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, right when Jii-chan got better, \NI get hit with a cold and tests.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.55,0:05:51.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Given all that, was I supposed to keep up \Nmy end and pull off regular robberies?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.08,0:05:53.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That third-rate inspector...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.06,0:05:57.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What does he think I am, a weekly \Nmanga magazine or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.60,0:05:58.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.78,0:06:00.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet he's dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.71,0:06:03.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's gotta be it! Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.74,0:06:06.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Talk about no tact...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.73,0:06:26.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've finally got my health back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.69,0:06:31.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All right. Time to look into \Nwhat the Young Master requested.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.57,0:06:38.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. That is indeed a valuable jewel...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.24,0:06:43.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...but at best, it's a gem \Nworth tens of millions,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.39,0:06:45.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,not a Big Jewel.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.20,0:06:52.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Young Master seems to be busy at school, \Nso I can save this report for another day.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.39,0:06:55.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,E-Everyone! It's Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.39,0:06:58.27,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Kid the Phantom Thief Has Issued a Notice?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.82,0:06:58.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kid the Phantom Thief has released a notice!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.49,0:07:04.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,At 6:54 pm this evening, Christmas Eve,\N Kid the Phantom Thief stole
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.65,0:07:07.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,the Star of the Giants that was decorating \NTofu Department Store's Christmas tree!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.65,0:07:11.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There it is! He finally struck!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.65,0:07:13.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}The star is inlaid with emeralds \Nworth several billion yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.30,0:07:16.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}It's meant to be donated to \Na museum after Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.52,0:07:17.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that's what I'm talkin' about, Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.96,0:07:22.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Inspector! Don't talk like that in public!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.92,0:07:28.17,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Drink. Drive. Lose Your License.\NTake Precautions Against Fire
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.10,0:07:24.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All cars, mobilize!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.61,0:07:26.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Get to the Tofu Department Store!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.52,0:07:28.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.65,0:07:37.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's all the fuss about?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.46,0:07:39.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Something must've happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.01,0:07:40.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe a crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.28,0:07:44.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, we have to get to my house.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.84,0:07:57.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Customers are coming in droves,\N just like I thought!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.45,0:08:03.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,With this many people, \Nsales should double... no, quadruple!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.44,0:08:07.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Releasing a fake letter \Nwas a stroke of genius.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.42,0:08:09.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But, sir...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.86,0:08:14.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If Kid doesn't actually show up, \Nwe'll lose face and sales afterwards...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.10,0:08:18.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kid the Phantom Thief wouldn't \Nlet his prey escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.72,0:08:21.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.34,0:08:23.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you get it yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.09,0:08:23.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.49,0:08:27.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're gonna play Kid the Phantom Thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.46,0:08:30.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,M-M-Me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.11,0:08:33.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Relax. I'll prepare your escape route.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.26,0:08:37.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But I don't know if I can \Ndo something so outrageous.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.44,0:08:40.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you steal that Star of the Giants,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.62,0:08:45.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,we can hold onto it {\i1}and{\i0} reap the huge \Nreward of the amount it's insured for.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.98,0:08:49.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And the whole thing will be pinned on Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.28,0:08:54.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Succeed, and I'll make you my vice-president.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.32,0:08:56.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,V-Vice-president?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.09,0:09:00.85,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Special Bonus
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.85,0:09:02.60,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Special Bonus
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.60,0:09:05.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think it's a bad deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.24,0:09:09.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.58,0:09:21.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'll do it, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.37,0:09:24.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I-Isn't that enough, Aoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.08,0:09:28.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang in there! You're so impatient.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.13,0:09:30.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This spot?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.38,0:09:33.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A-A little to the right...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.01,0:09:35.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Then here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.56,0:09:38.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez! That's left, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.58,0:09:39.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You suck at this, Kaito!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.97,0:09:42.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If we don't hurry, everyone \Nwill be here before it's done!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.51,0:09:44.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You{\i0} hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.51,0:09:47.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And you're heavy...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.10,0:09:49.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,For cryin' out loud, it's not \Nlike you're a little kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.70,0:09:53.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you gotta hold a \NChristmas party every year?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.23,0:09:55.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can do what I want!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.85,0:10:00.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You and your parties...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.77,0:10:05.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's excitement in the air \Nat Tofu Department Store.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.81,0:10:07.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There are two more hours \Nuntil the appointed time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.54,0:10:09.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, quit being lazy and help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.85,0:10:10.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.71,0:10:12.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Will he really come?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.71,0:10:12.96,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Kid the Phantom Thief Sent Advance Notice?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.96,0:10:16.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fork and spoon go opposite!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.51,0:10:18.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How the hell should I know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.51,0:10:22.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's interview Inspector Nakamori, \Nwho's in charge of security.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.84,0:10:26.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Inspector, Kid has made a move at last.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.61,0:10:31.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kid! I'll pulverize you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.49,0:10:32.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just you wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.96,0:10:35.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That was Inspector Nakamori, in high spirits.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.74,0:10:44.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You can see all the people gathered \Ndown below from our chopper camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.12,0:10:47.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you viewers at home \Nknow what this is about.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.66,0:10:51.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This crowd of onlookers has Kid fever!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.12,0:10:54.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no understatement to say that Kid is \Nthe greatest phantom thief of this generation!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.40,0:10:59.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.25,0:11:01.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.44,0:11:02.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the invite!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.93,0:11:04.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You came too, Akako-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.97,0:11:09.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I just thought it would be immature \Nnot to come after you invited me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.14,0:11:13.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm glad you all came. Come on in!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.52,0:11:17.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, did you hear? Kid is appearing tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.58,0:11:22.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Kid for you, showing up \Non Christmas Eve! That's awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.17,0:11:26.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. All that brouhaha was over\N Kid the Phantom Thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.62,0:11:33.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll get to see your dad all hot and \Nbothered with frustration again, Aoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.07,0:11:34.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.34,0:11:35.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.92,0:11:38.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.65,0:11:45.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.12,0:11:49.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kid! Kid! Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.56,0:11:52.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kid! Kid! Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.98,0:11:55.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kid! Kid! Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.56,0:12:00.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kid! Kid! Kid! Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.44,0:12:03.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Kid calls have begun!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.82,0:12:07.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kid! Kid! Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.09,0:12:08.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kid! Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.16,0:12:13.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Kid! I'm gonna be \Nthe one who captures you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.76,0:12:19.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't skip town on me \Nwithout previous notice!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.91,0:12:28.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Merry Christmas!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.30,0:12:30.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.18,0:12:35.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, I've got a lot of food over here,\N so everyone eat your fill.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.17,0:12:37.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! It looks delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.15,0:12:40.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She just put out store-bought stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.09,0:12:42.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No need to tell them that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.11,0:12:43.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got cake, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.94,0:12:44.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.91,0:12:51.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Flutter-flutter-flutter! And...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.04,0:12:52.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...look!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.20,0:13:00.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now who would be calling at a time like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.91,0:13:04.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Does anybody have a lighter?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.76,0:13:13.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, nobody here would have a lighter...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.55,0:13:16.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess we'll just have to \Nborrow one from Aoko's dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.96,0:13:19.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.10,0:13:27.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And I thought I'd have Dad sing us a song...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.10,0:13:32.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He said he's gonna be late tonight \Nbecause of Kid the Phantom Thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.36,0:13:35.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, good for him...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.37,0:13:37.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.14,0:13:39.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He scared me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.81,0:13:42.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm right here, so how could Kid...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.93,0:13:44.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're at Tofu Department Store.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.80,0:13:47.84,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Emergency live broadcast! \NThe appointed time is nigh!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.80,0:13:49.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kid T-shirts, sweatshirts, and other \Nmerchandise are selling like hotcakes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.30,0:13:55.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Mr. Zaizen, the owner \Nof Tofu Department Store.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.30,0:14:01.52,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Emergency live broadcast! \NThe appointed time is nigh!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.76,0:13:59.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are your thoughts on the advance \Nnotice you received from Kid today?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.44,0:14:01.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I was shocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.52,0:14:04.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't recall sending out \Nany advance notice!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.58,0:14:06.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this about?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.46,0:14:09.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't ask me! \NAnd... why {\i1}are{\i0} you asking me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.66,0:14:13.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito and Akako-chan! \NWhat are you whispering about?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.71,0:14:15.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.23,0:14:16.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.59,0:14:20.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But what about this \Nunexpectedly huge sales boost?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.04,0:14:26.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If they just got notice today, \Nwhy do they have all those Kid goods?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.84,0:14:32.05,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Emergency live broadcast! \NThe appointed time is nigh!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.37,0:14:32.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like Kid is everywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.53,0:14:37.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It just goes to show that even a sneak \Nthief like that can do some good!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.68,0:14:41.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.52,0:14:43.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Good grief...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.15,0:14:46.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kid is bad, but this owner is no better!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.77,0:14:47.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Kaito?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.38,0:14:50.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.04,0:14:56.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, he couldn't just stand here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.66,0:14:59.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kid! Kid! Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.66,0:14:59.66,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Emergency live broadcast! \NThe appointed time is nigh!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.66,0:15:03.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kid! Kid! Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.17,0:15:05.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to those cheers.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.48,0:15:05.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Kid! Kid! Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.97,0:15:09.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But Kid isn't here yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.08,0:15:09.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Kid! Kid! Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.05,0:15:12.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kid! Kid! Kid! Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.30,0:15:14.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kid! Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.31,0:15:19.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kid! Kid! Kid! Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.74,0:15:22.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kid! Kid! Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.62,0:15:27.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! What's he doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.33,0:15:30.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's already past the appointed time!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.17,0:15:46.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Kid! Kid the Phantom Thief is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.98,0:15:56.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.56,0:16:19.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you waiting for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.79,0:16:21.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.53,0:16:22.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is too much for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.96,0:16:25.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot! Vice-president! \NYou can be vice-president!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.29,0:16:30.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, that includes a major raise!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.80,0:16:36.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus a chauffeur and flexible working hours!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.14,0:16:46.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's not all! The vice-prez gets \Nto take home food from the gourmet floor!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.15,0:16:48.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'll do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.06,0:16:52.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to take the Star of the Giants!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.78,0:16:56.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kid! Kid! Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.16,0:17:00.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kid! Kid! Kid! Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.79,0:17:03.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kid! Kid! Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.09,0:17:07.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew he could do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.00,0:17:08.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I just had to hold his hand most of the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.62,0:17:13.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Farewell!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.22,0:17:19.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Give up, Kid the Phantom Thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.40,0:17:28.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.86,0:17:31.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What?! I've never seen \Nyou before in my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.73,0:17:33.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't do this to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.61,0:17:35.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know when to give up, Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.13,0:17:41.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kid the Phantom Thief, you're under arrest!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.88,0:17:43.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.87,0:17:46.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Kid isn't all he's cracked up to be!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.73,0:17:53.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, please continue to shop at \NTofu Department Store!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.10,0:18:05.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,K...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.31,0:18:07.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,K...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.14,0:18:09.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kid the Phantom Thief?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.40,0:18:16.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Merry Christmas, Inspector Nakamori!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.03,0:18:23.03,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}Good luck, Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.50,0:18:29.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Which is the real one?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.79,0:18:33.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.29,0:18:38.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I came, just as the advance \Nnotice stated, Mr. Zaizen.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.10,0:18:40.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And it's Christmas Eve.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.76,0:18:43.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A night when miracles can happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.48,0:18:45.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kid-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.76,0:18:47.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me a miracle, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.87,0:18:52.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll climb the tree, so wait \Nfor me up there, Kid-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.27,0:18:56.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-With a suave line like that, \Nthis must be the real Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.67,0:18:58.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.19,0:19:03.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-oh. But first, how about I \Ngive you a Christmas present?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.19,0:19:42.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,M-M-My department store!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.99,0:19:45.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm off...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.06,0:19:47.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait, Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.54,0:19:50.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you intend to vanish again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.13,0:19:58.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kid, back then...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.76,0:20:02.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...you suddenly disappeared \Nwithout any warning.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.22,0:20:06.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And eight years passed like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.60,0:20:09.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're going to do it again...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.64,0:20:18.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to run or hide,\N Inspector Nakamori.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.48,0:20:19.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's meet again!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.58,0:20:27.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.46,0:20:35.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,"Let's meet again," he says! The idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.96,0:20:39.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The next time we meet, I'll tan your hide!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.69,0:20:42.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You look happy, Inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.22,0:20:50.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.88,0:20:55.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Start to wind it up, you guys,\N before it gets late.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.90,0:20:58.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aoko, I'm starving!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.77,0:21:01.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,K-Kaito?! Where were you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.96,0:21:04.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry! I had to run an errand.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.65,0:21:08.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And on the way back, I bought an ornament \Nfor your tree, so cut me some slack!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.53,0:21:11.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So how about some grub?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.79,0:21:14.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm runnin' on empty here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.46,0:21:17.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We finished everything already!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.04,0:21:19.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.48,0:21:26.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You have it rough.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.69,0:21:34.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Couldn't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.58,0:21:47.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The program you witnessed this evening \Nwas the miracle of a holy night.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.45,0:21:49.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Truth that sprang from a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.53,0:21:53.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you enjoyed it, then I'm \Nsatisfied as a magician.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.64,0:21:57.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, see you next illusion!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.42,0:23:34.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi, Nakamori Aoko here! \NI'm doing the preview today!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.28,0:23:36.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In the next episode, we all go skiing!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.64,0:23:40.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Akako-chan puts the moves on Kaito \Non the pure white ski slope!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.84,0:23:43.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That Kaito is pretty popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.16,0:23:45.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what'll happen with those two.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.24,0:23:47.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And what'll happen with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.72,0:23:49.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, we enjoy \Na hot spring bath, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.65,0:23:53.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on {\i1}Magic Kaito 1412{\i0}: \NGet Away from Him!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.65,0:23:53.66,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Get Away from Him
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.66,0:23:56.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Step right this way! Watch carefully!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.58,0:23:58.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't miss the illusion!
